<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((الإرواء)</span>) <span class="c2">(٦٠٨ و ٦١١)</span> , <span class="c2">((أحكام الجنائز)</span>) <span class="c2">(ص٢٩ - ٣٠)</span> , <span class="c2">((خطبة الحاجة)</span>) <span class="c2">(ص٣٤ - ٣٥)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>